reviews.text: Awful very dirty, needs a complete revamp..

Very dark and dirty, strong smells of old urine as you go up the stairs. You can see it being riddled with germs so i wouldn't touch the handrail, i wouldn't touch anything. No staff and no information boards. Just disgusting. I will not be stopping off at this station again.

The person who was working the office today was extremely rude ,, all I wanted to do was ask a question regarding a train and he refused speak shook his head and said in finished closed I said only need to ask a question and he said no , consequently after I had gone down the stairs and asked a passenger I had to come back out ,, I'm registered disabled ,, shocking service,, 
What makes it worse I had just had to walk 🚶 from moorside station as the person in that office was just as bad and as rude
May not be the best station in the world but it serves the local community well.
Train services and frequency are good
